{"tid":1181146,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"為六九做好準備","createTime":"2019-06-01T11:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T17:14:25.000Z","uid":160261,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bcfb3b261f3e39b38f969a9565c37f37c39fc27b","tid":1181146,"uid":160261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"雨傘個陣，我記得好多人好冇做好準備，戴個口罩就去迎戰。點知...<br />\n<br />\n如今仲有個幾禮拜，係時候準備下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 自製防毒面具<br />\n<img src=\"http://survival-mastery.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Homemade-gas-mask.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsurvival-mastery.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2FHomemade-gas-mask.jpg&h=c5b9d528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instructables.com/id/DIY-Gas-Mask/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instructables.com%2Fid%2FDIY-Gas-Mask%2F&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTvvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=4405d76b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instructables.com/id/DIY-Gas-Mask/</a><br />\n基本上只係要個大膠樽，電線膠紙，口罩就得。有冇用我唔知，不過有好過冇。<br />\n<br />\n2. 洗碗手套<br />\n催淚彈好熱，戴好手套先好掂，最好就掟走。<br />\n<br />\n3. 雨嬲<br />\n減少皮膚同化學物質既接觸。<br />\n<br />\n4. 單車護具<br />\n細個學單車有頭盔，護踭同護膝。有就最好帶埋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/711lijNSzUL._SX466_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F711lijNSzUL._SX466_.jpg&h=fd11adb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入討論，準備呢家野唔怕多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36768ea78da493ffc37184c4bf16da3215375233","tid":1181146,"uid":160261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T11:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p